{
  "video_id": "3P-2dcS19fk",
  "title": "Scientists must be free to learn, to speak and to challenge | Kirsty Duncan",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12920.0,
      "end_time": 16640.0,
      "text": "Let me tell you about rock snot."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 19800.0,
      "end_time": 22616.0,
      "text": "Since 1992, Dr. Max Bothwell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22640.0,
      "end_time": 25656.0,
      "text": "a Government of Canada scientist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25680.0,
      "end_time": 30616.0,
      "text": "has been studying a type of algae that grows on rocks."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 30640.0,
      "end_time": 37216.0,
      "text": "Now, the very unscientific term for that algae is rock snot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 37240.0,
      "end_time": 39656.0,
      "text": "because as you can imagine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 39680.0,
      "end_time": 42360.0,
      "text": "it looks a lot like snot."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 43800.0,
      "end_time": 48736.0,
      "text": "But scientists also call it Didymosphenia geminata"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 48760.0,
      "end_time": 53960.0,
      "text": "and for decades, this algae has been sliming up riverbeds"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 53120.0,
      "end_time": 55256.0,
      "text": "around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 55280.0,
      "end_time": 57816.0,
      "text": "The problem with this algae"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 57840.0,
      "end_time": 61736.0,
      "text": "is that it is a threat to salmon, to trout"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 61760.0,
      "end_time": 65416.0,
      "text": "and the river ecosystems it invades."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 65440.0,
      "end_time": 68655.0,
      "text": "Now, it turns out Canada&#39;s Dr. Bothwell"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 68680.0,
      "end_time": 72856.0,
      "text": "is actually a world expert in the field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 72880.0,
      "end_time": 77560.0,
      "text": "so it was no surprise in 2014"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 77800.0,
      "end_time": 80536.0,
      "text": "when a reporter contacted Dr. Bothwell"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 80560.0,
      "end_time": 83800.0,
      "text": "for a story on the algae."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 83880.0,
      "end_time": 90536.0,
      "text": "The problem was, Dr. Bothwell wasn&#39;t allowed to speak to the reporter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 90560.0,
      "end_time": 95296.0,
      "text": "because the government of the day wouldn&#39;t let him."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 95320.0,
      "end_time": 98735.0,
      "text": "110 pages of emails"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 98760.0,
      "end_time": 102696.0,
      "text": "and 16 government communication experts"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 102720.0,
      "end_time": 105880.0,
      "text": "stood in Dr. Bothwell&#39;s way."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 106800.0,
      "end_time": 110560.0,
      "text": "Why couldn&#39;t Dr. Bothwell speak?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 110800.0,
      "end_time": 112896.0,
      "text": "Well, we&#39;ll never know for sure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 112920.0,
      "end_time": 116656.0,
      "text": "but Dr. Bothwell&#39;s research did suggest"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 116680.0,
      "end_time": 120536.0,
      "text": "that climate change may have been responsible"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 120560.0,
      "end_time": 123800.0,
      "text": "for the aggressive algae blooms."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 123920.0,
      "end_time": 130920.0,
      "text": "But who the heck would want to stifle climate change information, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 132240.0,
      "end_time": 134560.0,
      "text": "Yes, you can laugh."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 134800.0,
      "end_time": 135976.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a joke,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 136000.0,
      "end_time": 137840.0,
      "text": "because it is laughable."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 139760.0,
      "end_time": 145176.0,
      "text": "We know that climate change is suppressed for all sorts of reasons."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 145200.0,
      "end_time": 149456.0,
      "text": "I saw it firsthand when I was a university professor."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 149480.0,
      "end_time": 155160.0,
      "text": "We see it when countries pull out of international climate agreements"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 155400.0,
      "end_time": 159176.0,
      "text": "like the Kyoto Protocol and the Paris Accord,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 159200.0,
      "end_time": 164399.0,
      "text": "and we see it when industry fails to meet its emissions reduction targets."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 165400.0,
      "end_time": 170696.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not just climate change information that&#39;s being stifled."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 170720.0,
      "end_time": 177376.0,
      "text": "So many other scientific issues are obscured by alternate facts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 177400.0,
      "end_time": 182176.0,
      "text": "fake news and other forms of suppression."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 182200.0,
      "end_time": 184416.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve seen it in the United Kingdom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 184440.0,
      "end_time": 186376.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve seen it in Russia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 186400.0,
      "end_time": 189160.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve seen it in the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 189400.0,
      "end_time": 191775.0,
      "text": "and, until 2015,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 191800.0,
      "end_time": 194480.0,
      "text": "right here in Canada."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 195840.0,
      "end_time": 198656.0,
      "text": "In our modern technological age,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 198680.0,
      "end_time": 202856.0,
      "text": "when our very survival depends on discovery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 202880.0,
      "end_time": 205656.0,
      "text": "innovation and science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 205680.0,
      "end_time": 209816.0,
      "text": "it is critical, absolutely critical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 209840.0,
      "end_time": 213856.0,
      "text": "that our scientists are free to undertake their work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 213880.0,
      "end_time": 217176.0,
      "text": "free to collaborate with other scientists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 217200.0,
      "end_time": 219775.0,
      "text": "free to speak to the media"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 219800.0,
      "end_time": 222816.0,
      "text": "and free to speak to the public."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 222840.0,
      "end_time": 224616.0,
      "text": "Because after all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 224640.0,
      "end_time": 230696.0,
      "text": "science is humanity&#39;s best effort at uncovering the truth"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 230720.0,
      "end_time": 232256.0,
      "text": "about our world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 232280.0,
      "end_time": 235160.0,
      "text": "about our very existence."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 235400.0,
      "end_time": 237696.0,
      "text": "Every new fact that is uncovered"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 237720.0,
      "end_time": 243536.0,
      "text": "adds to the growing body of our collective knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 243560.0,
      "end_time": 247296.0,
      "text": "Scientists must be free to explore"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 247320.0,
      "end_time": 251696.0,
      "text": "unconventional or controversial topics."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 251720.0,
      "end_time": 255376.0,
      "text": "They must be free to challenge the thinking of the day"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 255400.0,
      "end_time": 256696.0,
      "text": "and they must be free"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 256720.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263800.0,
      "text": "to present uncomfortable or inconvenient truths,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 264400.0,
      "end_time": 267215.0,
      "text": "because that&#39;s how scientists push boundaries"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 267240.0,
      "end_time": 272255.0,
      "text": "and pushing boundaries is, after all, what science is all about."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 272279.0,
      "end_time": 274376.0,
      "text": "And here&#39;s another point:"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 274400.0,
      "end_time": 278856.0,
      "text": "scientists must be free to fail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 278880.0,
      "end_time": 283736.0,
      "text": "because even a failed hypothesis teaches us something."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 283760.0,
      "end_time": 288936.0,
      "text": "And the best way I can explain that is through one of my own adventures."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 288960.0,
      "end_time": 291919.0,
      "text": "But first I&#39;ve got to take you back in time."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 293000.0,
      "end_time": 295456.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the early 1900s"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 295480.0,
      "end_time": 299480.0,
      "text": "and Claire and Vera are roommates in southern Ontario."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 300520.0,
      "end_time": 304775.0,
      "text": "One evening during the height of the Spanish flu pandemic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 304800.0,
      "end_time": 307240.0,
      "text": "the two attend a lecture together."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 308280.0,
      "end_time": 312335.0,
      "text": "The end of the evening, they head for home and for bed."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 312360.0,
      "end_time": 315576.0,
      "text": "In the morning, Claire calls up to Vera"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 315600.0,
      "end_time": 318400.0,
      "text": "and says she&#39;s going out to breakfast."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 319800.0,
      "end_time": 322335.0,
      "text": "When she returns a short while later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 322360.0,
      "end_time": 324336.0,
      "text": "Vera wasn&#39;t up."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 324360.0,
      "end_time": 327376.0,
      "text": "She pulls back the covers"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 327400.0,
      "end_time": 330000.0,
      "text": "and makes the gruesome discovery."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 330720.0,
      "end_time": 332840.0,
      "text": "Vera was dead."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 334240.0,
      "end_time": 336576.0,
      "text": "When it comes to Spanish flu,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 336600.0,
      "end_time": 338816.0,
      "text": "those stories are common,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 338840.0,
      "end_time": 342376.0,
      "text": "of lightning speed deaths."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 342400.0,
      "end_time": 345496.0,
      "text": "Well, I was a professor in my mid-20s"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 345520.0,
      "end_time": 349960.0,
      "text": "when I first heard those shocking facts"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 349120.0,
      "end_time": 353520.0,
      "text": "and the scientist in me wanted to know why and how."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 355160.0,
      "end_time": 359256.0,
      "text": "My curiosity would lead me to a frozen land"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 359280.0,
      "end_time": 361895.0,
      "text": "and to lead an expedition"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 361920.0,
      "end_time": 366960.0,
      "text": "to uncover the cause of the 1918 Spanish flu."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 366120.0,
      "end_time": 372376.0,
      "text": "I wanted to test our current drugs against one of history&#39;s deadliest diseases."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 372400.0,
      "end_time": 375176.0,
      "text": "I hoped we could make a flu vaccine"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 375200.0,
      "end_time": 378455.0,
      "text": "that would be effective against the virus"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 378480.0,
      "end_time": 380136.0,
      "text": "and mutation of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 380160.0,
      "end_time": 382400.0,
      "text": "should it ever return."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 384280.0,
      "end_time": 389150.0,
      "text": "And so I led a team, a research team,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 389400.0,
      "end_time": 391576.0,
      "text": "of 17 men"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 391600.0,
      "end_time": 395536.0,
      "text": "from Canada, Norway, the United Kingdom"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 395560.0,
      "end_time": 397416.0,
      "text": "and the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 397440.0,
      "end_time": 401656.0,
      "text": "to the Svalbard Islands in the Arctic Ocean."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 401680.0,
      "end_time": 406160.0,
      "text": "These islands are between Norway and the North Pole."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 406400.0,
      "end_time": 408240.0,
      "text": "We exhumed six bodies"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 409280.0,
      "end_time": 413455.0,
      "text": "who had died of Spanish flu and were buried in the permafrost"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 413480.0,
      "end_time": 418720.0,
      "text": "and we hoped the frozen ground would preserve the body and the virus."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 419600.0,
      "end_time": 422176.0,
      "text": "Now, I know what you are all waiting for,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 422200.0,
      "end_time": 425320.0,
      "text": "that big scientific payoff."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 426240.0,
      "end_time": 431800.0,
      "text": "But my science story doesn&#39;t have that spectacular Hollywood ending."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 432800.0,
      "end_time": 434536.0,
      "text": "Most don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 434560.0,
      "end_time": 438376.0,
      "text": "Truth is, we didn&#39;t find the virus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 438400.0,
      "end_time": 441575.0,
      "text": "but we did develop new techniques"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 441600.0,
      "end_time": 444216.0,
      "text": "to safely exhume bodies"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 444240.0,
      "end_time": 446320.0,
      "text": "that might contain virus."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 446920.0,
      "end_time": 449616.0,
      "text": "We did develop new techniques"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 449640.0,
      "end_time": 452216.0,
      "text": "to safely remove tissue"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 452240.0,
      "end_time": 455256.0,
      "text": "that might contain virus."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 455280.0,
      "end_time": 458535.0,
      "text": "And we developed new safety protocols"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 458560.0,
      "end_time": 464216.0,
      "text": "to protect our research team and the nearby community."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 464240.0,
      "end_time": 467736.0,
      "text": "We made important contributions to science"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 467760.0,
      "end_time": 471256.0,
      "text": "even though the contributions we made"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 471280.0,
      "end_time": 474400.0,
      "text": "were not the ones originally intended."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 475280.0,
      "end_time": 478416.0,
      "text": "In science, attempts fail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 478440.0,
      "end_time": 481560.0,
      "text": "results prove inconclusive"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 481800.0,
      "end_time": 483520.0,
      "text": "and theories don&#39;t pan out."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 484360.0,
      "end_time": 485720.0,
      "text": "In science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 487320.0,
      "end_time": 491496.0,
      "text": "research builds upon the work and knowledge of others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 491520.0,
      "end_time": 493560.0,
      "text": "or by seeing further,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 493800.0,
      "end_time": 496960.0,
      "text": "by standing on the shoulders of giants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 496120.0,
      "end_time": 498816.0,
      "text": "to paraphrase Newton."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 498840.0,
      "end_time": 502455.0,
      "text": "The point is, scientists must be free"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 502480.0,
      "end_time": 506496.0,
      "text": "to choose what they want to explore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 506520.0,
      "end_time": 508736.0,
      "text": "what they are passionate about"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 508760.0,
      "end_time": 512000.0,
      "text": "and they must be free to report their findings."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 513200.00000000006,
      "end_time": 514456.00000000006,
      "text": "You heard me say"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 514480.0,
      "end_time": 520696.0,
      "text": "that respect for science started to improve in Canada in 2015."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 520720.0,
      "end_time": 522736.0,
      "text": "How did we get here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 522760.0,
      "end_time": 525760.0,
      "text": "What lessons might we have to share?"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 526520.0,
      "end_time": 530976.0,
      "text": "Well, it actually goes back to my time as a professor."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 531000.0,
      "end_time": 536576.0,
      "text": "I watched while agencies, governments and industries around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 536600.0,
      "end_time": 541136.0,
      "text": "suppressed information on climate change."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 541160.0,
      "end_time": 543415.0,
      "text": "It infuriated me."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 543440.0,
      "end_time": 545696.0,
      "text": "It kept me up at night."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 545720.0,
      "end_time": 552000.0,
      "text": "How could politicians twist scientific fact for partisan gain?"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 553560.0,
      "end_time": 558215.0,
      "text": "So I did what anyone appalled by politics would do:"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 558240.0,
      "end_time": 561536.0,
      "text": "I ran for office, and I won."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 561560.0,
      "end_time": 567815.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 567840.0,
      "end_time": 571376.0,
      "text": "I thought I would use my new platform"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 571400.0,
      "end_time": 575136.0,
      "text": "to talk about the importance of science."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 575160.0,
      "end_time": 580496.0,
      "text": "It quickly became a fight for the freedom of science."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 580520.0,
      "end_time": 585776.0,
      "text": "After all, I was a scientist, I came from the world under attack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 585800.0,
      "end_time": 588719.0,
      "text": "and I had personally felt the outrage."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 590800.0,
      "end_time": 595656.0,
      "text": "I could be a voice for those who were being silenced."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 595680.0,
      "end_time": 600550.0,
      "text": "But I quickly learned that scientists were nervous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 600800.0,
      "end_time": 602816.0,
      "text": "even afraid to talk to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 602840.0,
      "end_time": 605616.0,
      "text": "One government scientist, a friend of mine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 605640.0,
      "end_time": 607199.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ll call him McPherson,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 608920.0,
      "end_time": 611896.0,
      "text": "was concerned about the impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 611920.0,
      "end_time": 616136.0,
      "text": "government policies were having on his research"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 616160.0,
      "end_time": 620616.0,
      "text": "and the state of science deteriorating in Canada."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 620640.0,
      "end_time": 623816.0,
      "text": "He was so concerned, he wrote to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 623840.0,
      "end_time": 626816.0,
      "text": "from his wife&#39;s email account"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 626840.0,
      "end_time": 630456.0,
      "text": "because he was afraid a phone call could be traced."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 630480.0,
      "end_time": 634776.0,
      "text": "He wanted me to phone his wife&#39;s cell phone"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 634800.0,
      "end_time": 637856.0,
      "text": "so that call couldn&#39;t be traced."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 637880.0,
      "end_time": 639920.0,
      "text": "I only wish I were kidding."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 641200.0,
      "end_time": 647336.0,
      "text": "It quickly brought what was happening in Canada into sharp focus for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 647360.0,
      "end_time": 652560.0,
      "text": "How could my friend of 20 years be that afraid to talk to me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 653360.0,
      "end_time": 656160.0,
      "text": "So I did what I could at the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 656400.0,
      "end_time": 660000.0,
      "text": "I listened and I shared what I learned"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 661720.0,
      "end_time": 664256.0,
      "text": "with my friend in Parliament,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 664280.0,
      "end_time": 668216.0,
      "text": "a man who was interested in all things environment, science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 668240.0,
      "end_time": 670840.0,
      "text": "technology, innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 672120.0,
      "end_time": 676176.0,
      "text": "And then the 2015 election rolled around"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 676200.0,
      "end_time": 679376.0,
      "text": "and our party won."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 679400.0,
      "end_time": 681576.0,
      "text": "And we formed government."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 681600.0,
      "end_time": 683320.0,
      "text": "And that friend of mine"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 685120.0,
      "end_time": 688816.0,
      "text": "is now the Prime Minister of Canada, Justin Trudeau."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 688840.0,
      "end_time": 694456.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 694480.0,
      "end_time": 698936.0,
      "text": "And he asked if I would serve as his Minister of Science."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 698960.0,
      "end_time": 701776.0,
      "text": "Together, with the rest of the government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 701800.0,
      "end_time": 707856.0,
      "text": "we are working hard to restore science to its rightful place."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 707880.0,
      "end_time": 713296.0,
      "text": "I will never forget that day in December 2015"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 713320.0,
      "end_time": 716336.0,
      "text": "when I proudly stood in Parliament"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 716360.0,
      "end_time": 717696.0,
      "text": "and proclaimed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 717720.0,
      "end_time": 721600.0,
      "text": "\"The war on science is now over.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 722720.0,
      "end_time": 728296.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 728320.0,
      "end_time": 732576.0,
      "text": "And I have worked hard to back up those words with actions."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 732600.0,
      "end_time": 735560.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve had many successes."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 735800.0,
      "end_time": 737200.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s still more work to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 738640.0,
      "end_time": 741960.0,
      "text": "because we&#39;re building this culture shift."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 741120.0,
      "end_time": 747560.0,
      "text": "But we want our government scientists to talk to the media, talk to the public."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 747800.0,
      "end_time": 750536.0,
      "text": "It&#39;ll take time, but we are committed."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 750560.0,
      "end_time": 756935.0,
      "text": "After all, Canada is seen as a beacon for science internationally."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 756960.0,
      "end_time": 759280.0,
      "text": "And we want to send a message"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 760560.0,
      "end_time": 764815.0,
      "text": "that you do not mess with something so fundamental,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 764840.0,
      "end_time": 767640.0,
      "text": "so precious, as science."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 769680.0,
      "end_time": 774695.0,
      "text": "So, for Dr. Bothwell, for Claire and Vera,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 774720.0,
      "end_time": 778296.0,
      "text": "for McPherson and all those other voices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 778320.0,
      "end_time": 784136.0,
      "text": "if you see that science is being stifled, suppressed or attacked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 784160.0,
      "end_time": 785856.0,
      "text": "speak up."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 785880.0,
      "end_time": 791536.0,
      "text": "If you see that scientists are being silenced, speak up."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 791560.0,
      "end_time": 795376.0,
      "text": "We must hold our leaders to account."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 795400.0,
      "end_time": 799256.0,
      "text": "Whether that is by exercising our right to vote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 799280.0,
      "end_time": 803616.0,
      "text": "whether it is by penning an op-ed in a newspaper"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 803640.0,
      "end_time": 808496.0,
      "text": "or by starting a conversation on social media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 808520.0,
      "end_time": 814496.0,
      "text": "it is our collective voice that will ensure the freedom of science."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 814520.0,
      "end_time": 819136.0,
      "text": "And after all, science is for everyone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 819160.0,
      "end_time": 825896.0,
      "text": "and it will lead to a better, brighter, bolder future for us all."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 825920.0,
      "end_time": 827136.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 827160.0,
      "end_time": 831800.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}